#===================== HR Management ====================#

Modules
=======

Admin Module
-------------
    1: Dashboard (Template)

        // Tabular:
        // New Updates from consultancy
        (Manage/View)

        hyperlink -> consultancy (Template: Manage Consultancy)
        hyperlink -> candidate (Template: Manage Candidate)
        Other Details (**)

    2: Manage Consultancy (Template)

        // Manage consultancy profiles

        1: Accept consultancy request (Registration)
        2: Delete consultancy request (Registration)

    3: Manage Candidate (Template)

        // View and evaluate candidate interview videos and resumes

        1: Interview Video (Download/View)
        2: Resume (Download/View)
        3: Other details (If any)

    4: Requirements (Template)

        // add requirements like questionare for interview and required candidate details

        1: Questionnaire (Create/Update/Delete)
        2: Candidate Details (Create/Update/Delete)

    5: Settings (Template) (Optional)

        // General settings for the admin



Consultancy Module
------------------

    1: Dashboard (Template)

        // To view the new requirements from Admin (HR)
        // Tabular

        1: Candidate Profiles (Status/ Interviewed/ Waiting ...)
            Hyperlink -> Manage Canidate (Template)

        2: New Requierements (Questionnaires & Candidate details)

    2: Manage Candidate (Template)

        // Add Profiles of candiadates, Upload videos, resumes, other details (If any)

        1: Manage Candidate Profiles (Add/Update/Delete)

        ** Dynamic forms or tables can add details like
            i) Interview videos
            ii) Resumes
            iii) Other details (If any)